  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>The Arrow represents the journey; the travels needed to reach a destination, through all factors of life. The Arrow's Folly depicts their failure, and the natural instinct to shy away from hardship to remarkable degrees.</p><p><strong>Constellation</strong> @UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.deities.Item.bQJ4eQKF50ofQdGr]{The Arrow}</p><hr /><p><strong>First Asterism </strong>(Level 4): You can open the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.IDBB44egwiQ4qZNh]{Kinetic Gate} for Water and can use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.g8QrV39TmZfkbXgE]{Channel Elements} for it, which allows you to make @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.6lbr0Jnv0zMB5uGb]{Elemental Blast} with Water. If you already have the Kinetic Gate feature, you instead gain @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.vEiENk0IzuzRQesp]{Gate's Threshold} and Fork the Path to Water, which allows you to select a Water impulse feat. Regardless, anytime you reinvest this facet each day, you can select any of your choices.</p>"
    },
